1. We can apply shadow to our elements.

example
#file style.css
h1{
    text-shadow: 3px 5px 4px rgb(103, 205, 226),
        -3px -5px 4px rgb(237, 100, 100);
}

#box{
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background-color:bisque;
    box-shadow: 3px 5px 4px;
}


NOTE:

3px for horizontal
5px for vertical
4px for blur
